// APT hook for HestiaCP server.
//
// Re-applies the Exim PLAIN-authenticator fix after any apt/dpkg operation,
// so a HestiaCP/Exim package update that overwrites
// /etc/exim4/exim4.conf.template cannot silently break authenticated relay
// to the KumoMTA smart host. The fix script is idempotent, so running it on
// every transaction is a no-op once already applied.
//
// Install to (on the HestiaCP server):
//   /etc/apt/apt.conf.d/99-hestia-exim-plain-fix
DPkg::Post-Invoke { "/usr/local/sbin/hestia-exim-plain-fix.sh || true"; };
